{"tid":494066,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"ADHD點學英文好","createTime":"2017-12-09T08:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T16:40:39.000Z","uid":162397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"64c62d2cf6e770f7add8d111a8d2bef066818f1c","tid":494066,"uid":162397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買晒d 練習 發現自己覺得好悶 好難認真做"},{"pid":"7f26817e567923485c2491ff44a2eba0d6e103ab","tid":494066,"uid":138526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"ADHD here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c6477e49dde6065755967d623c2ef9cfd15a93","tid":494066,"uid":34301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買晒d 練習 發現自己覺得好悶 好難認真做</blockquote><br />\n畀啲目標自己<br />\n最重要就係啲目標係具體同埋實踐到嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n大目標：英文考試90分以上<br />\n<br />\n中期目標：明白點運用passive voice<br />\n<br />\n細目標：<br />\n星期一  睇passive voice練習前面啲summary同埋做十至二十題，做完對答案<br />\n星期二  問返自己passive voice有咩特性同埋幾時用，睇埋琴日錯過啲咩之後就另外再做十至二十題，做完對答案<br />\n星期三  再問返自己passive voice嘅基本特性同埋自己常犯嘅錯誤係咩，跟住再比較passive voice同英文裡面唔同嘅concept，例如比較下passive voice同active voice，另外再做revision exercise，做完對答案<br />\n星期四  喺啲blog或者articles裡面搵下啲人有冇用到passive voice，如果你覺得佢係用緊/錯passive voice，解釋返點解佢係用緊/錯passive voice。<br />\n星期五  總結返自己學過同錯過嘅嘢（一定要做呢步，唔做呢步唔會深化到之前學過嘅嘢）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上嘅嘢我自己都未做過，所以話唔到畀你聽呢個方法有冇用，但係有五樣好重要嘅，一定要記住做<br />\n<br />\n1) 定下具體同埋實踐到嘅目標<br />\n2) 比較不同概念<br />\n3) 設想不同例子<br />\n4) 嘗試解釋<br />\n5) 作結"},{"pid":"381dc3aa916fc59810d481b6dd7e666382400263","tid":494066,"uid":162397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"Thanks&not;&not;&not;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0b8261043bc7ec91725678f663955a38a4d754","tid":494066,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:34:02.000Z","msg":"Adhd咩黎"},{"pid":"cfdef99fb71d3388f2d8a9f1d5dce6d5fc06de4a","tid":494066,"uid":62469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"唔好話學英文,就算好似我學鋼琴咁,我都坐唔定"},{"pid":"80d7ba7249421a5c192c512b204177e765a65133","tid":494066,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"Adhd+1 讀書個陣去油麻地玉器市場隔離覆診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n成日覺得溫書唔定 唔知係個病定係懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801185aeff701de2acf74eb9bc5e48b72caa81b3","tid":494066,"uid":85307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"食完藥都唔得?"},{"pid":"2fd5c7e25381556c858920d518b9d646cbbad00e","tid":494066,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"食下藥囉"},{"pid":"0506379d6b6350d1fac0d2ae5bb080ddda6374e1","tid":494066,"uid":162397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食完藥都唔得?</blockquote><br />\nyes 食完ok 就唔洗問了~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab82c52548d4c3a2506f5f75f90b6201e9772a8","tid":494066,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"asso degree high dip？？"},{"pid":"d005b6f6bdbe872b0fa7c7cf9b57009f7b99779b","tid":494066,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1857053/%E5%B0%88%E6%B3%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%81%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%AA%B2%E6%98%93%E6%B8%B8%E9%AD%82%20%20%20%20%20%E6%A3%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E8%B2%BC%E5%A3%ABKO%E7%B9%81%E5%BF%99%E